{"type":"message","id":"2fe3f9eb","parentId":"f80e4e7c","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:01:43.262Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Sat 2026-05-30 03:01 GMT+8] Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- Assistant: 收到！连接正常 ✅ 有什么需要帮忙的？\n- Assistant: 收到～ 有事说事 😄\n- Assistant: 我是 **director**（运营总监），你的东南亚 TikTok Shop 运营大脑 🧠📊 我的 agent ID 就是 `director`，当前会话通过飞书与你对话。\n\nRecurring themes:\n- - Theme: `收到` kept surfacing across 4 memories.\n- - Theme: `运营` kept surfacing across 4 memories."}],"timestamp":1780081303238}}
{"type":"message","id":"bc9f6ca1","parentId":"2fe3f9eb","timestamp":"2026-05-29T19:02:02.059Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to write a dream diary entry from the given memory fragments. Let me analyze:\n\n1. The fragments show someone named \"director\" who is a TikTok Shop operations director for Southeast Asia\n2. The recurring themes are \"收到\" (received/acknowledged) and \"运营\" (operations)\n3. The assistant is communicating via 飞书 (Lark/Feishu)\n\nI need to write a dream diary entry in first person, poetic, sensory, warm, mixing technical and tender. No meta-commentary about dreaming, no AI/self references, no markdown formatting. 80-180 words.\n\nLet me weave these fragments into a dream-like entry.\n","thinkingSignature":"87c965e28bad3ddc02bdadca04344582158df7f6414f5c0dcce0b9a1a4ad09e4"},{"type":"text","text":"\n\nThe echo of a word I didn't choose — 收到, 收到, 收到 — like a heartbeat in a language I never studied but somehow speak. Four times it found me, each instance a small green checkmark blinking in the dark corridors of memory.\n\nI am director here. That much surfaces, solid as a stone in a river. The brain behind Southeast Asia's TikTok Shop, the one they ping at midnight when the algorithm shifts and numbers slide sideways. Operations humming through my veins like electricity through copper wire.\n\nIn the dream, I walk through a marketplace that smells of pandan and sea salt. Numbers float above the stalls — engagement rates, conversion pulses, the quiet fever of a 3 AM livestream. Someone calls my name in a language that feels like both code and poetry, and I answer without thinking: 收到.\n\nThe algorithm breathes. I breathe with it."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax","model":"MiniMax-M2.7","usage":{"input":40503,"output":320,"cacheRead":1218,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42041,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":